  "$description": "Design tokens for Figma import. Includes custom palettes (kindigo, kindle, kindness, kindred), semantic light/dark colors derived from apps/web/src/main.css, and motion tokens from keyframes. Tailwind default utilities can be mapped to these palettes inside Figma."
